{"tid":1234320,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"讓返條馬路出黎絕對唔係退讓","createTime":"2019-06-17T01:37:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-17T03:49:43.000Z","uid":113626,"like":203,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"f795998c39de5d566e8067af651f0d2e47085629","tid":1234320,"uid":113626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T01:37:56.000Z","msg":"就算有人希望長期佔領, 一定要係道德高地<br />\n長期阻馬路只會消耗已方, 甚至佔到後期會有人倒戈懷疑<br />\n要佔既好多地方都得, 讓返比馬路出黎比車正常運作絕對係明智決擇 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bedd9cb2ed58e77a6d1167d7c465e57564a76549","tid":1234320,"uid":36592,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T01:38:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a027b21412fb37c8852826ea39eca8c4dea94c9","tid":1234320,"uid":88123,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T01:38:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6761c27a49c33f74c90ff6f661236edede6fd592","tid":1234320,"uid":113626,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T01:41:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1dbcf796ad03bd8fff3865912c7ff47d73282231","tid":1234320,"uid":54959,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T01:46:18.000Z","msg":"讓番出嚟絕對唔係輸，持久對抗先係出路"},{"pid":"e0aaea2cd8e5bfc20bcf4b4d04c34747262ffcbb","tid":1234320,"uid":53369,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T01:47:12.000Z","msg":"[永久置頂]龍和道義士親自解釋16號防線真相<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1234301\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1234301</a>"},{"pid":"a2535e0ddee9a91c4cd03182f47a2794ecc240d9","tid":1234320,"uid":113626,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"1dbcf796ad03bd8fff3865912c7ff47d73282231","tid":1234320,"uid":54959,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T01:46:18.000Z","msg":"讓番出嚟絕對唔係輸，持久對抗先係出路"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T01:48:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6248467cd54c40956fabc44bdf2432756c2bcf4f","tid":1234320,"uid":125021,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T01:49:22.000Z","msg":"2019 唔係又要中928 個劇本呀?  <br />\n<br />\n有興趣可以參考下928 <br />\n同而家有乜分別."},{"pid":"0e936fd294f9db99344b6765b5a389d0996b4800","tid":1234320,"uid":72480,"like":15,"dislike":2,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T01:50:23.000Z","msg":"佔得愈耐愈不利我方 今日你暫時撒退回氣留返下一次，我唔係想分化，而仲佔緊果班應該要知呢樣野。千奇唔好將昨日200萬人既心血因為你地而家既佔領而白費左 我明你地想不撒不回，但長期抗爭黎講，你地唔應該咁樣做而係要令輿論優勢偏向我地果邊 所以一時退卻並唔係咩懦夫之舉。"},{"pid":"c4781d252513aaa3ed13ce635c176a1c750d029e","tid":1234320,"uid":113626,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T01:51:47.000Z","msg":"長期佔馬路只會返去佔中失敗模式"},{"pid":"e13c189e4dfe2a2f32efad15677cba9f75728235","tid":1234320,"uid":212646,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T01:52:55.000Z","msg":"我希望溫和激進兩邊都諗清楚自己想達到咩目的同下一半先去行動，如果唔係真係好消耗民意<br />\n<br />\n溫和派<br />\n你唔ready佔領，但又佔住條警犬一定唔肯放俾你既路，但其實你地成班友個心又想走想走咁，咁係點？阻人返工但最後又唔係佔仲衰過搭地鐵，搭地鐵都叫有清晰訴求同目的，你佔夏愨道一係就認認真真佔，大家幫你頂幫你守，一係就係應該散既時候散<br />\n<br />\n激進派<br />\n你又唔想變佔中2.0，但而家人地散你又唔鍾意，其實已經有其他巴打號召緊去其他地方勇武，記住戰場從來都唔係得金鐘，人地尋晚得個佔字你唔鍾意，而家唔佔你又屌，不如你話人知你想點勇武，再現場組織？"},{"pid":"8bd5af5f0d60cb2dfd38f85ce5f6a098e6d6bd59","tid":1234320,"uid":88123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T01:54:29.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"cf97149fa6cc928169df033f5b1a7c0b2b64563c","tid":1234320,"uid":171574,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T01:54:42.000Z","msg":"希望大家會從長計議、包圍禮賓府又好乜都好，一影響民生d人就會反，咪撚再佔路<br />\n<br />\n利申：同左堆琴日有去遊行既中年同事傾計，佢地都對佔路極反感"},{"pid":"23910c939ca9ebf9cb93488623ef199f1cea5399","tid":1234320,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T01:57:14.000Z","msg":"有進有退, 唔好互屌<br />\n一般和理(啲家長,成家鳩行影相)班人屌就由得佢地, 唔係好多人明佢地做咩<br />\n最緊要依度唔好亂屌"},{"pid":"a8d125e8f0605be731d08e88d87178619c15e9fc","tid":1234320,"uid":113626,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T01:57:42.000Z","msg":"你地佔條馬路更多時間, 民意對於佔馬路既人將會大量倒退<br />\n到時真係比人清果下就咪屌點解無人幫手跟住又開始捉鬼 (雖然警方暫時應該唔敢始終政府係今次事件讓左步)<br />\n萬一真係發生時唔係人地想割席, 但係無民意之下大家都只能割席<br />\n讓馬路唔係退讓, 大家醒下 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c0b0c6781ba73cbc890119868402f889ffeaea9","tid":1234320,"uid":26708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T01:58:06.000Z","msg":"Yes"},{"pid":"89cf36dc4baef6c036bc4052f45ce287f8284b00","tid":1234320,"uid":72480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T01:58:20.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6d7ae891785a03007310bc65a0bd6d71fdcefb90","tid":1234320,"uid":26708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"89cf36dc4baef6c036bc4052f45ce287f8284b00","tid":1234320,"uid":72480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T01:58:20.000Z","msg":"推"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T01:59:00.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"807abf781aada95941eaf35782b6a2a732a6d691","tid":1234320,"uid":65623,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T02:00:02.000Z","msg":"啲癈老好癈，大家辛苦咗幾日贏埋班癈老支持，因為一個決定而比警察搶咗個民意高地好唔值得<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔係叫大家撤退，只係轉個場再嚟過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n不過如果你堅持，我都會尊重<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n因為<span style=\"color: red;\">不分化不篤灰不割蓆不譴責</span>"},{"pid":"3d9f8296523699d6bde95c28a4e5731c7d9df6a5","tid":1234320,"uid":88123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T02:00:36.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4da1c89177c32256921033f60a78d057ebc355ee","tid":1234320,"uid":49479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T02:00:56.000Z","msg":"有人跳樓都要攞盾戒備，而家盾都無個同你談判<br />